wow guys (kstin, court, tor, meg, meg, darcy, and laura) that was awesome last night!  i am really tired now though....  megHAN - whats the word? word up!  lol and word to your mother! yeah thaty was wicked funny! darcy - lets foam at the mouth! kstin thanks for delivering my 6 kids! lol the butterfly chair really helped! omg we are soo weird!  but the morning of the sleepover was awesome too cause i went shopping with my mom and i got new puma shoes! they are really cool.  they're brown suede with a creame little stripe thing....  yeah i am really excited about them!  thats all i guess. except for when i got home from laura's i cleaned mey room and wow you can actually see the clothes in my closet now! yeah i am soo proud!

-rachel

i stayed home from school today! it was awesome because i got to sleep in and then wake up and sleep some more! yes!!!!  the best thing of all is that i don't have ANY homewokr to make up! yes yes yes yes!  i am very excited even though i am sick!  the only bummer about today was that i didn't have any good food to eat so i ate like 1/4 of a bagut and a little bit of chicken noodle soup....  laura i can't wait till friday!  icecream sundaes! I LOVE ICECREAM SUNDAES!  well i am going to go and lay on the couch because i am oh so very lazy!
-rachel

wow, once again i havent writen in a while but thats ok cause i think i have a lot to write about today!  well yeah, report cards yesterday were great, i guess...  i got my first B ever! ever ever ever ever! but thats ok cause im in the 9th grade math so yeah.....  happy birthday to lauren today! yipee!  oooh yeah today we saw inca sun and they were really great, everyone really got into it!  so yeah and megan told me a secret that im not supposed to say until tomorow, so i wont tell until i can.... sorry.
oh yeah and if anyone drinks yoplait yogeurts you should have noticed the pink lids.  if you want to help fight breast cancer then bring me the clean lids!  thanks!  wow i am gonna go cause i have been really tired lately som i want to relax!

-rachel

hey..no school yesterday.. i slept over rach's wednesday night w/ victoria.. it was lotsa fun :o) french toast! haha goodtimes.ily. ummm then i came home and did homework :o( but then katie came over and me and my sis gave her the best present EVERR! the OC season 1 dvdss :o) then she watched the OC.. she left then i watched CSI then bedd.. school was okay i guess.. seemed like a short day cuz we got snow! :o) i<3snow! yayayaya! i have to teach ccd tomorrow morning.. funnnnnn yeah well thats all

<3laura
comment if you love mee<3

sean! i have that song stuck in my head! but it is soo cute it is okay that it is stuck in my head...  once again some people need to know that they aren't the only ohes in the room and that other people have feeling too!!!!!!!!!!!! ggrrhhhh! but thats ok cause i had a fun time in tech ed today! i am stronger than steve, i pulled apart the wood and he couldn't! ha i win!  tor and laura sorry i fell asleep wehn we were watchiong mean girls..... i was muy cansado....  tomorrow i go to my grandparents house fun fun fun!!!!!!!!  yeah so thats all. oh wait one more thing: mary kelley and sarah! awesome times kaing the movie yesterday! THE GAME OF ENLIGHTENMENT!  yipee
-rachel

hey! im so excited! today was wicked fun!!! dannys a freak but thats okay.. im just gunna stay away from him & so is tim! haha assembly today..boringgggg.. went to ms deveau during study and she went over my paragraphs with mee :o) yayy! shes the best teacher ever! im so excited for tonight!! RACH & VICTORIA!! --cant wait! ilysm! katies birthday is today :o) and tomorrow shes coming over to watch the OC and shes gunna get the greatest present and the greatest card EVER!!!!!! yay! im so excited! well im gunna go watch oprah :o) laterr..

<3laura

hey..stuffs been okay.. the bus drivers been giving me lip >:o/ ughhh well no mr. riley today :o) yayyyy! i talked to sonya today and im hoping i can get her to come back :o) i miss herr.. soo much homework lately and its not funn..not like homework ever is...ugh im ditching the bus tomorrow morning and im sleeping in :o) yay well im gunna go watch jepordy..<3

<3laura

some PEOPLE are really annoying me and they need to realize they are not the only people in the world! grrrrr.. but anyway i think i did good on my math quiz so thats a plus! i dont really have much to say except that i think i am getting a cold and i hate getting colds.... :(  o yeah laura i hope you dont have to go to mr rileys office again tomorrow that would stink!! i think i would cry if i had to go there, i hate confentation with mr riley he is soo intimidating..... lol jk but no i really do think i would cry!  (note: i hate waking up in the morning!!!!!!!!!!)  

-rachel-

hey.. today was pretty bad :o( >>i went to mr reillys office to support devin and dana but obviously mr. reilly didnt like what i had to say and it obviously had no affect on him whatsoever.. then the bus ride home was annoying.. devin and dana sat in the front so near the end me, eddie, kenny and katie are all gunna sit in the front because devin and dana did absolutely nothing.. yeah.. mrs deveaux just called to apologize for me getting called to the office :o) that was nice.. well i gotta gooo... CHADD IS THE COOOLEST PERSON EVERRRRRRRRRRRRR!!!!! hahaha

<3laura

(wow i havent written in a while) ALL of my cousins just left!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  they are soo annoying! one cousin (shes seven) was mad at my other cousins so she took a leaf and ripped it and said "mary that was you and now your dead" omg it was the funniest thing ever! lol she was soooo annoying then she kept slapping our butts!! whats up with that!?!?!?!i think she needs an attitude adjustment......  ahhhhhh i have a math quiz tomorrow! grrr i hope i dont fail.... no i know i wonT! I WILL BE POSITIVE I WILL NOT FAIL!!!!  yeah!  good mindset.....  well going to look for sfp topics! fun fun fun, actually i hate science fair projects with a passion! -rachel

ps: thanks soooo much to everyone who voted for me in the student council! i am soo excited ! thnk you so much!

<3laura

(mrs. bradley wasn't here today!!!!!!!!!!!!!!) the nurse gave me a freee icecream then i got another one at lunch! wow today was pretty darn good if you ask me! and sunday is going to be even better! i love halloween! yeah!
